ries.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20docuseries%20also%20notes%20that%20because%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bserial%20killer%26quot%3B%20hadn't%20been%20invented%20yet%2C%20the%20press%20and%20the%20public%20were%20convinced%20that%20only%20people%20with%20specific%20jobs%20or%20medical%20knowledge%20would%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20brutal%20murders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20episode%2C%20author%20and%20historian%20Paul%20Begg%20refers%20to%20%26quot%3Bthe%20deranged%20doctor%2C%20a%20midwife%2C%20a%20butcher%E2%80%A6%20Because%20they%20had%20various%20skills%20that%20Jack%20the%20Ripper%20had.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20person%20who%20fitted%20the%20description%20was%20an%20American%20man%20named%20Dr.%20Francis%20Tumblety.%20Per%20the%20UK's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwebarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk%2Fukgwa%2F20060711093022%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.met.police.uk%2Fhistory%2Fripper.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENational%20Archives%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20John%20George%20Littlechild%2C%20ex-detective%20chief%20inspector%20of%20the%20London%20Metropolitan%20Police%2C%20considered%20Tumblety%20a%20suspect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20YouTube%20video%20on%20Tumblety%20by%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4vDExNBHj4Q%26ab_channel%3DJackTheRipperTour%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Jack%20the%20Ripper%20Tour%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20is%20run%20by%20Jones%2C%20uses%20news%20clippings%20and%20archive%20documents%20to%20point%20to%20argue%20the%20was%20doctor%20misogynistic%2C%20including%20keeping%20jars%20of%20uteruses%20that%20had%20been%20surgically%20removed%20from%20women%20on%20shelves%20in%20his%20office.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.casebook.org%2Fsuspects%2Ftumblety.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Casebook%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20dedicated%20Ripper%20website%2C%20Tumblety%20was%20arrested%20for%20%26quot%3Bgross%20indecency%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20charged%20over%20what%20were%20known%20as%20the%20Whitechapel%20murders%20in%20November%201888.%20The%20five%20women%20killed%20by%20the%20Ripper%20are%20thought%20to%20have%20been%20part%20of%20the%2011%20victims%20that%20make%20up%20the%20Whitechapel%20murders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETumblety%20was%20given%20bail%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20US%20where%20he%20remained%20until%20he%20died%20in%201903%20in%20Rochester%2C%20New%20York.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMontague%20John%20Druitt%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221829%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20is%20a%20black-and-white%20photo%20of%20a%20man%20with%20a%20short%20mustache%20in%20a%20buttoned-up%20jacket%2C%20leaning%20on%20two%20books.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ab8499aab37011780c539e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221372%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20photo%20of%20Montague%20John%20Druitt%20seen%20in%20Netflix's%20%26quot%3BUnsolved%20Mysteries.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20series%20also%20presents%20Montague%20John%20Druitt%2C%20a%20barrister%20and%20a%20teacher%2C%20as%20a%20person%20of%20interest.%20He%20was%20dismissed%20from%20a%20London%20boarding%20school%20in%20November%201888%20for%20unknown%20reasons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20body%20was%20found%20in%20the%20Thames%20on%20December%2031%2C%201888%2C%20and%20he%20is%20thought%20to%20have%20died%20by%20suicide.%20The%20authorities%20looked%20at%20suspicious%20suicides%20after%20the%20Ripper%20killings%20stopped%20as%20a%20potential%20explanation%20for%20what%20happened%20to%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jack-the-ripper.org%2Fdruitt.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FJack-the-ripper.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJack-the-ripper.org%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20assistant%20chief%20constable%20Melville%20Macnaghten%20of%20the%20London%20Metropolitan%20Police%20wrote%20in%20a%20memorandum%20dated%201894%3A%20%26quot%3BFrom%20private%20information%20I%20have%20little%20doubt%20but%20that%20his%20own%20family%20suspected%20this%20man%20of%20being%20the%20Whitechapel%20murderer%2C%20it%20was%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20sexually%20insane.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Managhten%20never%20shared%20the%20information%20he%20claimed%20to%20have%2C%20and%20it%20is%20not%20known%20why%20Druitt's%20family%20suspected%20him%20of%20being%20the%20Ripper.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FJack-the-ripper.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJack-the-ripper.org%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20notes%20that%20the%20lead%20investigator%20of%20the%20murders%2C%20London%20Metropolitan%20Police%20inspector%20Frederick%20Abberline%2C%20doubted%20Druitt%20was%20the%20killer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201903%2C%20he%20told%20the%20Pall%20Mall%20Gazette%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20all%20about%20that%20story.%20But%20what%20does%20it%20amount%20to%3F%20Simply%20this.%20Soon%20after%20the%20last%20murder%20in%20Whitechapel%20the%20body%20of%20a%20young%20doctor%20was%20found%20in%20the%20Thames%2C%20but%20there%20is%20absolutely%20nothing%20beyond%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20was%20found%20at%20that%20time%20to%20incriminate%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAaron%20Kosminski%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221815%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sepia%20illustration%20of%20a%20man%20wearing%20a%20long%20coat%2C%20trousers%2C%20and%20a%20hat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ab86adfb6d32635ee59258%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221361%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20illustration%20of%20Aaron%20Kosminski%20in%20Netflix's%20%26quot%3BUnsolved%20Mysteries.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20episode%20briefly%20explains%20that%20the%20police%20identified%20a%20man%20called%20%26quot%3BAaron%20Kosminski%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20suspect%2C%20a%20Polish%20Jew%20who%20lived%20near%20where%20the%20murders%20happened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jack-the-ripper.org%2Fkosminski.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FJack-the-ripper.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJack-the-ripper.org%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Macnaghten%20concluded%20that%20Kosminski%20was%20a%20misogynist%20%E2%80%94%20although%20he%20doesn't%20state%20why%20%E2%80%94%20but%20said%20that%20his%20hatred%20of%20women%20made%20him%20a%20suspect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThis%20man%20became%20insane%20owing%20to%20many%20years%20indulgence%20in%20solitary%20vices.%20He%20had%20a%20great%20hatred%20of%20women%2C%20especially%20of%20the%20prostitute%20class%2C%20%26amp%3B%20had%20strong%20homicidal%20tendencies%3B%20he%20was%20removed%20to%20a%20lunatic%20asylum%20about%20March%201889%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20unclear%20what%20hard%20evidence%20the%20authorities%20had%20to%20suspect%20Kosminski.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20admitted%20to%20Colney%20Hatch%20Asylum%20in%201890%20after%20threatening%20his%20sister%20with%20a%20knife%2C%20according%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.casebook.org%2Fdissertations%2Frip-koshouse.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Caseb