%20con%20artist%20Anna%20Delvey%20(aka%20Anna%20Sorokin)%20who%20accused%20the%20fake%20socialite%20of%20conning%20her%20out%20of%20%2462%2C000%2C%20sued%20Netflix%20over%20its%20series%20%26quot%3BInventing%20Anna%2C%26quot%3B%20alleging%20the%20show%20portrayed%20her%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreedy%2C%20snobbish%2C%20disloyal%2C%20dishonest%2C%20cowardly%2C%20manipulative%20and%20opportunistic%20person.%26quot%3B%20The%20streamer%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rollingstone.com%2Ftv-movies%2Ftv-movie-news%2Fnetflix-inventing-anna-defamation-lawsuit-1234995042%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20lost%20its%20bid%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case%20in%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20New%20York%20City%20prosecutor%20Linda%20Fairstein%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fentertainment-arts%2Fbusiness%2Fstory%2F2024-06-04%2Fnetflix-ava-duvernay-linda-fairstein-when-they-see-us-lawsuit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esettled%20with%20Netflix%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Ava%20DuVernay%20in%20June%202024%20after%20she%20disputed%20her%20portrayal%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvillain%26quot%3B%20in%20%26quot%3BWhen%20They%20See%20Us%2C%26quot%3B%20DuVernay's%20award-winning%202019%20limited%20series%20about%20the%201989%20Central%20Park%20jogger%20case%2C%20which%20Fairstein%20famously%20prosecuted%20(she%20was%20portrayed%20by%20Felicity%20Huffman%20on%20the%20show).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20pending%20suits%20involve%20Netflix's%20unscripted%20docuseries.%20Buster%20Murdaugh%2C%20the%20son%20of%20convicted%20murderer%20Alex%20Murdaugh%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Fbuster-murdaugh-sues-netflix-warner-bros-saying-was-falsely-accused-mu-rcna157783%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20sued%20Netflix%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20allegations%20made%20against%20him%20in%20the%20docuseries%20%26quot%3BMurdaugh%20Murders%3A%20A%20Southern%20Scandal%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20R.%20Kelly's%20former%20assistant%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20Netflix%20and%20Lifetime%20in%20February%20for%20painting%20her%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bsinister%20and%20defamatory%20light%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20docuseries%20%26quot%3BSurviving%20R.%20Kelly%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20aired%20on%20both%20the%20streamer%20and%20the%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what's%20different%20here%3F%20Harvey's%20lawyer%2C%20Richard%20Roth%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20phone%20interview%20that%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20unique%20case%20because%20Netflix%20didn't%20market%20it%20as%20a%20fictionalized%20drama%20or%20say%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bbased%20on%26quot%3B%20a%20true%20story.%20Instead%2C%20the%20show's%20title%20card%20called%20it%20a%20true%20story%20outright%20from%20the%20opening%20moments%20of%20the%20first%20episode.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Gadd%20took%20pains%20to%20emphasize%20on%20his%20press%20tour%20that%20the%20series%20was%20%26quot%3Bemotionally%20true%26quot%3B%20to%20his%20experience%20and%20not%20a%20line-by-line%20retelling%20of%20events%2C%20Netflix's%20marketing%2C%20which%20highlighted%20things%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fnetflix%2Fstatus%2F1779162630520729877%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20show's%20use%20of%20real%20emails%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gadd%20says%20his%20stalker%20sent%20him%2C%20fed%20the%20%26quot%3Btrue%20story%26quot%3B%20intrigue.%20Ultimately%2C%20viewers%20were%20compelled%20to%20play%20detective%20and%20go%20searching%20for%20the%20real%20Martha%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDefamation%20lawsuits%20are%20common%20%E2%80%93%20but%20not%20all%20of%20them%20get%20this%20much%20press%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHollywood%20has%20been%20dramatizing%20true%20stories%20for%20as%20long%20as%20it%20has%20existed.%20The%20difference%20in%20the%20beginning%20was%20that%20most%20of%20the%20subjects%20were%20long%20dead%3A%20there%20are%20dozens%20of%20films%20about%20the%20real%20Macbeth%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20and%20Joan%20of%20Arc%2C%20each%20telling%20the%20story%20in%20a%20slightly%20different%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20got%20a%20little%20more%20tangled%20once%20writers%20started%20dramatizing%20stories%20involving%20people%20who%20were%20still%20alive.%20One%20of%20the%20earliest%20examples%20of%20a%20case%20filed%20by%20an%20individual%20against%20a%20major%20media%20company%20was%20Street%20v.%20NBC%2C%20tried%20in%20Tennessee%20in%20July%201977.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20has%20similar%20echoes%20to%20the%20defamation%20lawsuits%20we%20see%20today.%20Victoria%20Street%20(formerly%20Victoria%20Price)%20sued%20the%20network%20over%20her%20portrayal%20in%20%26quot%3BJudge%20Horton%20and%20the%20Scottsboro%20Boys%2C%26quot%3B%20a%201976%20docudrama%20that%20recounted%20one%20of%20the%20many%20trials%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbs.org%2Fwgbh%2Famericanexperience%2Ffeatures%2Fscottsboro-ruby-bates-and-victoria-price%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighly%20publicized%20Scottsboro%20case%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20which%20she%20and%20another%20white%20woman%20named%20Ruby%20Bates%20accused%20nine%20Black%20teenage%20boys%20of%20raping%20them%20on%20a%20train%20forty%20years%20earlier.%20Eight%20of%20the%20nine%20were%20sentenced%20to%20death%20for%20the%20crime%20despite%20a%20lack%20of%20medical%20evidence%2C%20but%20none%20were%20executed%20after%20Bates%20recanted%20her%20testimony%20and%20the%20accused%20received%20new%20trials%20on%20appeals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStreet%2C%20who%20never%20recanted%20her%20testimony%2C%20took%20offense%20to%20the%20way%20she%20was%20portrayed%20and%20sued%20the%20network%20on%20charges%20of%20libel%20and%20invasion%20of%20privacy%2C%20arguing%20that%20she%20was%20no%20longer%20a%20public%20figure.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1982%2F10%2F19%2Fobituaries%2Fvictoria-p-street-dies-at-77-a-figure-in-scottsboro-case.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20case%20was%20ultimately%20settled%3C%2Fa%3E%20out%20of%20court%2C%20and%20Street%20died%20at%2077%20a%20few%20years%20later%20in%201982.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScores%20more%20defamation%20lawsuits%20have%20been%20filed%20in%20the%20years%20since%2C%20against%20everything%20from%20the%202013%20Michael%20Bay%20movie%20%26quot%3BPain%20%26amp%3B%20Gain%26quot%3B%20(the%20real%20kidnapping%20victim%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbusiness-news%2Fhollywood-docket-clemency-project-erin-887395%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edidn't%20like%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20the%20character%20based%20on%20him%20was%20portrayed%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20unlikeable%2C%20sleazy%2C%20rude%2C%20abrasive%20braggart%26quot%3B)%20to%20the%202017%20FX%20drama%20%26quot%3BFeud%3A%20Bette%20and%20Joan%26quot%3B%20(Hollywood%20legend%20Olivia%20de%20Havilland%2C%20then%20101%2C%20would%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffilm%2F2018%2Fmar%2F16%2Ffeud-olivia-de-havilland-sues-fx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreferred%20to%20be%20excluded%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20this%20narrative).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20streaming%20wars%20in%20the%20late%202010s%2C%20there%20was%20a%20rush%20to%20produce%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fd18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net%2FCIK-0001065280%2Fc5e64982-659f-4726-97c9-c57767c3bec3.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompelling%20content%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20win%20the%20largest%20share%20of%20subscribers.%20And%20while%20we're%20still%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-hollywood-remakes-franchises-avatar-percy-jackson-one-piece-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretreading%20(and%20re-retreading)%20old%20IP%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20always%20chasing%20the%20dangling%20carrot%20of%20the%20ever-elusive%20Original%20Idea%2C%20more%20and%20more%20shows%20are%20riffing%20on%20true%20events.%20Except%20instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20historical%20figures%20(though%20there's%20plenty%20of%20that%20too)%2C%20they're%20increasingly%20about%20contemporary%20stories%20and%20people%20who%20arguably%20aren't%20hugely%20public%20personas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20unlike%20Macbeth%20and%20Joan%20of%20Arc%2C%20those%20people%20will%20absolutely%20sue%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHarvey's%20lawsuit%20may%20not%20deter%20Netflix%20from%20making%20more%20shows%20like%20this%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnflx-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%20is%20an%20incredibly%20lucrative%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20presumably%20deep%20pockets%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20settled%20with%20everyone%20from%20a%20Georgian%20chess%20grandmaster%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2022%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fnetflix-queens-gambit-lawsuit-settlement-nona-gaprindashvili-1235361680%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewho%20says%20she%20was%20defamed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Queen's%20Gambit%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20former%20New%20York%20prosecutor%20Fairstein%20for%20%26quot%3BWhen%20They%20See%20Us%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgriselda-blanco-family-settles-lawsuit-against-netflix-sofia-vergara-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrug%20queenpin%20Griselda%20Blanco's%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20%26quot%3BGriselda.%26quot%3B%20Whether%20they%20fight%20Harvey's%20case%20in%20court%20or%20opt%20to%20settle%2C%20the%20amount%20it%20would%20cost%20to%20do%20either%20won't%20bankrupt%20them.%20That%20much%20we%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20question%20is%20whether%20the%20sheets%20are%20balanced%20in%20the%20end%3A%20Would%20the%20cost%20of%20legal%20fees%20and%20a%20potential%20settlement%20or%20damages%20be%20more%20or%20less%20than%20what%20Netflix%20has%20made%20off%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer%26quot%3B%3F%20If%20it's%20more%2C%20will%20that%20stop%20Netflix%20and%20others%20from%20making%20more%20of%20these%20legally%20risky%20but%20creatively%20compelling%20shows%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarvey's%20lawyer%20Roth%20doesn't%20think%20Netflix%20particularly%20cared%20about%20the%20risk%20of%20legal%20action%20when%20it%20greenlit%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20they%20say%2C%20'We're%20going%20to%20make%20so%20much%20money%20on%20this.%20If%20someone%20sues%20us%2C%20let%20them%20sue%20us%2C'%26quot%3B%20Roth%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20an%20argument%20to%20be%20made%20that%20any%20press%2C%20even%20a%20lawsuit%2C%20is%20good%20press.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20have%20any%20inside%20knowledge%20about%20Netflix%20in%20particular%2C%20but%20I%20can%20say%20this%3A%20This%20is%20a%20very%20unique%20time%20for%20streamer%20wars%2C%20and%20Disney%2B%20and%20Netflix%20and%20all%20these%20companies%20trying%20to%20land%20on%20top%2C%20or%20Netflix%20trying%20to%20stay%20on%20top%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeff%20Lewis%2C%20a%20First%20Amendment%20attorney%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20could%20be%20for%20this%20window%20of%20time%2C%20while%20there's%20some%20uncertainty%20as%20to%20which%20streamer%20will%20survive%2C%20perhaps%20Netflix%20might%20be%20more%20willing%20to%20take%20a%20risk%20and%20get%20more%20attention%20and%20eyeballs%20on%20their%20screens%20in%20exchange%20for%20paying%20some%20lawyer%20fees.%20Who%20knows%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20there's%20a%20chance%20Netflix%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20hefty%20settlement%20to%20make%20the%20Harvey%20situation%20go%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20streamer%20has%20the%20advantage%20of%20the%20suit%20being%20filed%20in%20California%2C%20which%20has%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20robust%20pro-defendant%20defamation%20laws%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Lewis%20says.%20The%20case%20could%20be%20dismissed%20if%20Netflix%20brings%20and%20wins%20an%20anti-SLAPP%20motion%2C%20which%20would%20dismiss%20the%20case%20and%20make%20Harvey%20responsible%20for%20paying%20all%20of%20Netflix's%20legal%20fees.%20(As%20of%20writing%2C%20Netflix%20hasn't%20filed%20one.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20Netflix%20doesn't%20file%20an%20anti-SLAPP%20motion%2C%20or%20does%20file%20one%20and%20doesn't%20win%20it%2C%20Harvey%20could%20potentially%20see%20a%20payout%20anywhere%20from%20%24200%2C000%20all%20the%20way%20into%20%26quot%3Bmid-seven%20figures%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Lewis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJackie%20Ward%2C%20a%20Los%20Angeles-based%20entertainment%20attorney%20specializing%20in%20rights%20and%20clearances%2C%20points%20to%20the%20million-dollar%20donation%20Netflix%20made%20to%20the%20Innocence%20Project%20as%20part%20of%20Fairstein's%20settlement%20for%20%26quot%3BWhen%20They%20See%20Us%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20comparable%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Netflix%20to%20make%20something%20where%20they%20think%20that%20they%20do%20have%20some%20sort%20of%20liability%2C%20to%20make%20that%20go%20away%20for%20something%20like%20a%20million%20dollars%2C%20it's%20probably%20worth%20it%20to%20them%20for%20a%20company%20of%20that%20size%2C%26quot%3B%20Ward%20says.%20%26quot%3BA%20smaller%20distributor%2C%20maybe%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-reindeer-true-story-netflix-lawsuit-defamation-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722596943000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a15889fb2b6bedb05a3ee1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-reindeer-true-story-netflix-lawsuit-defamation-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fiona%20Harvey's%20lawsuit%20against%20Netflix's%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Reindeer%26quot%3B%20isn't%20the%20first%20defamation%20case%20against%20a%20TV%20show.%20But%20it%20coul