g%20the%20innocent.%20It%20warned%20that%20arresting%20the%20innocent%20while%20letting%20the%20guilty%20go%20free%20would%20be%20a%20grave%20injustice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20apologised%20but%20blamed%20media%20reports%20for%20the%20negative%20impression.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20directed%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20provide%20a%20clear%20account%20of%20the%20facts%2C%20stating%20that%20failing%20to%20do%20so%20would%20be%20unacceptable%20and%20likened%20it%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bbrothers%20club%26quot%3B%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cops%20were%20directed%20to%20conduct%20the%20investigation%20in%20a%20scientific%20manner%20and%20advised%20not%20to%20bow%20to%20to%20any%20external%20pressures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20asked%20why%20the%20civic%20officials%20didn't%20inform%20the%20commissioner%20about%20non-functioning%20storm%20water%20drains%20in%20Rajinder%20Nagar%2C%20adding%C2%A0it%20has%20%26quot%3Bbecome%20a%20norm%20and%20MCD%20officials%20are%20not%20bothered%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20arrested%20the%20owner%20and%20the%20coordinator%20of%20the%20Rau's%20IAS%20Study%20Circle%20and%20charged%20them%20for%20culpable%20homicide%20after%20three%20students%20-%20Shreya%20Yadav%20(25)%20of%20Ghaziabad%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Tanya%20Soni%20(25)%20from%20Telangana%20and%20Nevin%20Delvin%20(24)%20from%20Ernakulam%20in%20Kerala%20-%20died%20in%20its%20flooded%20basement%20on%20Saturday%20night%20in%20Old%20Rajinder%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20have%20said%20an%20absence%20of%20a%20drainage%20system%20and%20safety%20measures%20and%20the%20use%20of%20the%20basement%20for%20commercial%20activities%20in%20violation%20of%20norms%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20three%20civil%20services%20aspirants%20at%20the%20coaching%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722595860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fhiikkt3o_upsccoach