ard%20X%20for%20price%20Y%3F%20There%20has%20to%20be%20data%20for%20SIT%20to%20probe%20this...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20setting%20up%20a%20SIT%20is%20not%20the%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EElectoral%20Bonds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotified%20by%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20in%20January%202018%2C%20this%20was%20pitched%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20cash%20donations%20made%20to%20political%20parties%20as%20part%20of%20its%20efforts%20to%20bring%20in%20transparency%20in%20political%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-bjp-congress-trinamool-vedanta-megha-engineering-future-gaming-who-gave-most-to-each-party-electoral-bonds-infra-firm-mining-telecom-g-5291114%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInfra%20Firm%2C%20Mining%2C%20Telecom%20Giant%20Are%20BJP's%20Largest%20Bonds%20Donors%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20court%20called%20the%20scheme%20unconstitutional%20and%20said%20information%20about%20political%20funding%20is%20essential%20for%20voters%20to%20make%20electoral%20choices.%20Such%20a%20system%20-%20meaning%20electoral%20bonds%20-%20could%20lead%20to%20governments%20tweaking%20national%20policies%20in%20favour%20of%20donors%2C%20many%20of%20which%20were%20large%20corporates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-never-claimed-this-was-the-absolute-way-pm-modi-on-electoral-bonds-scheme-5447372%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20Will%20Regret%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20On%20Scrapping%20Of%20Electoral%20Bonds%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20insisted%20the%20scheme%2C%20though%20not%20perfect%2C%20helped%20eliminate%20black%20money%2C%20referring%20to%20unaccounted%20cash%20or%20funds%20from%20criminal%20acti