%20more%20people.%20We%20have%20been%20looking%20everywhere.%20Some%20people%20are%20scared%20of%20coming%20out%20of%20their%20houses.%20There%20must%20be%20people%20who%20are%20unable%20to%20contact%20for%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20searching%20for%20bodies%20too%2C%20unfortunately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20total%20number%20of%20dead%20has%20been%20given%20by%20the%20district%20officials%3B%20however%2C%20the%20army%20and%20others%20in%20the%20area%20have%20recovered%20120%20bodies.%20%26quot%3BThe%20number%20of%20dead%20is%20much%20more.%20These%20are%20only%20the%20bodies%20we%20have%20recovered%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20looking%20at%20deploying%20radar%20equipment.%20We%20already%20have%20sniffer%20dogs%20working%20to%20find%20bodies%20buried%20deep%2C%26quot%3B%20Major%20General%20Mathew%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThermal%20scanners%20are%20also%20being%20used%2C%20but%20it%20has%20limited%20effectiveness%20as%20dead%20bodies%20do%20not%20emit%20heat%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20rescue%20workers%20had%20made%20temporary%20wooden%20bridges%20between%20landmasses%20to%20cross%20and%20help%20stranded%20people.%20However%2C%20those%20temporary%20structures%20failed%20during%20heavy%20rain%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20materials%20for%20building%20the%20bridge%20were%20flown%20into%20Kannur%20airport%20from%20Delhi%20and%20Bengaluru%20and%20brought%20to%20Wayanad%20by%2017%20trucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescuers%20continue%20to%20race%20against%20time%20under%20harsh%20conditions%20to%20search%20for%20survivors%20trapped%20in%20collapsed%20buildings.%20The%20total%20number%20of%20dead%20has%20crossed%20290.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722595020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2ho0fn6o_bailey-bridge_625x300_02_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fground-report-