0It's%20one%20thing%20to%20know%20this%20in%20theory%3B%20it's%20quite%20another%20to%20see%20the%20stark%20difference%20between%20gross%20and%20net%20pay%20on%20your%20very%20own%20paycheck.%20And%2C%20of%20course%2C%20six%20figures%20only%20goes%20so%20far%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20Still%2C%20I%20had%20enough%20money%20to%20save%20properly%2C%20while%20also%20enjoying%20my%20life%20in%20a%20way%20I%20hadn't%20had%20the%20privilege%20to%20do%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%2C%20I%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20that%20first%20tech%20job%20after%20about%20a%20year.%20I%20survived%20off%20unemployment%20insurance%20and%20a%20decent%20severance%20package%20and%20as%20soon%20as%20my%20severance%20ran%20out%2C%20I%20was%20offered%20another%20six-figure%20job%20at%20a%20marketing%20agency.%20It%20was%20a%20little%20less%20than%20I%20made%20before%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20good%20money.%20The%20cosmic%20timing%20made%20me%20feel%20good%2C%20and%20we%20continued%20with%20the%20lavish%20lifestyle%20sprinkled%20with%20Dom%20Perignon%20champagne.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217d857dd-db4a-4a42-8a8e-b6bd432775a8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20laid%20off%20again%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20next%20layoff%20took%20about%20six%20months%2C%20and%20the%20severance%20wasn't%20nearly%20as%20cushy.%20I%20was%20shaking%20with%20a%20combination%20of%20shock%2C%20rage%2C%20confusion%2C%20and%20fear%20as%20the%20two-person%20panel%20told%20me%20with%20long%20faces%20that%20my%20position%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Baffected%20by%20a%20reduction%20of%20workforce.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20the%20general%20advice%20is%20to%20have%20at%20least%20six%20months%20of%20savings.%20%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20saved%20that%20suggested%20amount%20of%20money%20and%20then%20some%2C%20and%20I%20still%20ran%20out%20of%20money.%20I%20exhausted%20the%20unemployment%2C%20maxed%20out%20credit%20cards%2C%20severely