ity-anti-aging-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupplement%3C%2Fa%3E%20capsules%20all%20promising%20to%20keep%20them%20young%2C%20vibrant%2C%20and%20strong%2C%20even%20as%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20(FDA)%20has%20technically%20banned%20many%20of%20these%20supplements%20from%20being%20sold%20while%20they%20are%20still%20being%20tested%20clinically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223270%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hailey%20bieber%20in%20front%20of%20the%20eiffel%20tower%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669aa75780d4d5da13d57b00%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224905%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHailey%20Bieber%2C%20a%2027-year-old%20model%2C%20has%20injected%20NAD.%20%3Cp%3EStephane%20Cardinale%20-%20Corbis%2FCorbis%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENAD%20supplements%20promise%20to%20replenish%20your%20body's%20natural%20supply%20of%20a%20critical%20molecule%20called%20nicotinamide%20adenine%20dinucleotide%20(NAD).%20It's%20one%20major%20component%20of%20healthy%20bodies.%20We%20create%20it%20ourselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNAD%20coenzymes%20are%20the%20central%20catalysts%20of%20all%20living%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Charles%20Brenner%2C%20a%20biochemist%20who%20studies%20NAD%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThey%20underlie%20the%20conversion%20of%20protein%2C%20fat%2C%20and%20carbohydrate%20into%20energy.%20They%20underlie%20the%20conversion%20of%20everything%20that%20we%20eat%20into%20everything%20that%20we%20do%20and%20everything%20that%20we%20are.%20They%20are%20required%20for%20our%20cells%20to%20generate%20energy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENAD%20is%20life-and-death%20important.%20Without%20the%20proper%20vitamins%20and%20minerals%20for%20creating%20it%2C%20people%20develop%20diarrhea%2C%20brain%20issues%2C%20red%2C%20scaly%20skin%2C%20and%20eventually%20waste%20away%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhistory.nih.gov%2Fpages%2Fviewpage.action%3FpageId%3D8883184%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edie%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20high%20levels%20of%20it%2C%20you%20may%20feel%20just%20a%20little%20sharper%2C%20more%20well-rested%2C%20and%20energetic.%20In%20short%3A%20Young.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20age%2C%20our%20bodies%20become%20less%20efficient%20at%20doing%20many%20things%2C%20including%20producing%20NAD.%20So%20while%20your%20average%2020-year-old%20can%20generate%20more%20than%20enough%20NAD%20from%20food%20and%20activity%2C%20most%2060-%20or%2070-year-olds%20might%20benefit%20from%20a%20booster.%20Whether%20it%20does%20anything%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-wellness-influencer-is-shady-untrustworthy-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealth%20influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20athletes%2C%20and%20wellness%20buffs%20in%20their%2030s%2C%2040s%2C%20and%2050s%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%2C%20many%20NAD-boosting%20supplements%20don't%20work.%20You%20need%20to%20know%20a%20lot%20about%20your%20chosen%20product%20%E2%80%94%20and%20yourself%20%E2%80%94%20to%20understand%20how%20successful%20any%20%26quot%3Bboost%26quot%3B%20will%20turn%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b3d7af5-df14-4d8e-ad4f-d7d0fce7c803%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20several%20different%20ways%20to%20boost%20NAD%20%E2%80%94%20but%20some%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20ones%20don't%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22powders%2C%20pills%2C%20supplements%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66aab73cfb6d32635ee58415%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFarion_O%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENutrition%20experts%20have%20known%20for%20nearly%20a%20century%20how%20important%20this%20coenzyme%20is%20to%20our%20health.%20It's%20the%20reason%20all-purpose%20flour%20and%20cereal%20are%20enriched%20with%20niacin%2C%20a%20common%20NAD%20precursor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20wasn't%20until%20the%20past%20two%20decades%20that%20a%20groundbreaking%20body%20of%20research%20started%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F15137942%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemerge%3C%2Fa%3E%20showing%20that%20NAD-boosted%20mice%20can%20not%20only%20survive%20and%20thrive%2C%20but%20can%20actually%20live%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10738409%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elonger%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20less%20fat%2C%20more%20musculature%2C%20lower%20inflammation%2C%20and%20fewer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1126%2Fscience.aac4854%3Furl_ver%3DZ39.88-2003%26rfr_id%3Dori%3Arid%3Acrossref.org%26rfr_dat%3Dcr_pub%2520%25200pubmed%23sec-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eage-related%20issues%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20roughly%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20scientists%20started%20taking%20these%20products%20out%20of%20their%20labs%20and%20developing%20NAD-boosting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elysiumhealth.com%2Fpages%2Fmission%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompanies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That's%20when%20NAD%20boosters%20really%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrobiotech.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etook%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20longevity-seekers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20lab%20rats%20to%20gym%20rats%2C%20boosting%20your%20NAD%20levels%20is%20no%20longer%20something%20just%20for%20mice%20in%20cages.%20Anyone%20remotely%20linked%20to%20longevity%20innovation%20is%20at%20least%20thinking%20about%20trying%20this%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20in%20this%20industry%3A%20billionaires%2C%20biohackers%2C%20brilliant%20scientists%20from%20the%20best%20schools%2C%20but%20you%20also%20have%20athletes%20and%20beautiful%20people%2C%20and%20people%20who%20just%20generally%20want%20to%20stay%20young%2C%26quot%3B%20Robert%20Fried%2C%20a%20moviemarker-turned-CEO%20of%20NAD%20supplement%20company%20ChromaDex%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20(Brenner%20is%20ChromaDex's%20chief%20science%20officer.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFried%20says%20NAD%20boosting%20is%20generally%20good%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20you%20want%20to%20increase%20your%20resiliency.%26quot%3B%20Maybe%20you're%20jet-lagged%2C%20you%20pulled%20an%20all-nighter%2C%20or%20you're%20feeling%20just%20a%20little%20bit%20sick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a84e4387-adc8-4ea3-963e-d72f3732c16e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20boost%20NAD%2C%20don't%20take%20NAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20drinking%20a%20pink%20protein%20shake.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66796396d1c84a0eaca6feb0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20is%20a%20plethora%20of%20various%20powders%2C%20pills%2C%20and%20IV%20drips%20all%20promising%20to%20boost%20NAD.%20Some%20may%20work%2C%20and%20some%20definitely%20don't.%20%3Cp%3EAleksandarNakic%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%20want%20to%20boost%20your%20NAD%20levels%2C%20there's%20no%20point%20in%20taking%20NAD%20as%20a%20supplement.%20The%20NAD%20molecule%20is%20just%20too%20big%20to%20be%20taken%20up%20by%20our%20cells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20pretty%20useless%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Sabine%20Donnai%2C%20a%20physician%20who%20has%20been%20testing%20out%20formulations%20of%20NAD%20boosters%20for%20her%20patients%20at%20the%20posh%20Viavi%20longevity%20clinic%20in%20London%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20She's%20discovered%2C%20through%20blood%20tests%2C%20that%20NAD%20supplements%20and%20IVs%20don't%20work%20much%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndependent%20experts%20like%20Dr.%20Shin-ichiro%20Imai%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20developmental%20biology%20at%20Washington%20University%20School%20of%20Medicine%20in%20St.%20Louis%20who's%20been%20studying%20NAD%20for%20decades%2C%20agree%20with%20Donnai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20NAD%20itself%20is%20not%20as%20effective%20as%20other%20compounds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20big%20and%20it%20cannot%20actually%20easily%20go%20into%20cells.%20And%20also%2C%20if%20you%20take%20NAD%20orally%2C%20your%20gut%20bacteria%20basically%20consume%20NAD%20completely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20most%20scientists%20say%20it's%20far%20more%20effective%20to%20take%20NAD%20precursors%20%E2%80%94%20the%20stuff%20that%20our%20bodies%20use%20to%20create%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3ENAD.%20That%20includes%20nicotinamide%20riboside%2C%20nicotinamide%20mononeucleotide%2C%20nicotinic%20acid%2C%20and%20niacinamide.%20(For%20those%20in%20the%20know%2C%20that's%20NR%2C%20NMN%2C%20niacin%2C%20and%20NAM.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ced299e9-0003-4b78-9444-08228e34c728%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20boost%20your%20NAD%20without%20an%20IV%20drip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222038%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22meat%2C%20fish%2C%20proteins%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66aab791fb6d32635ee58419%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221472%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChicken%2C%20fish%2C%20and%20edamame%20all%20help%20boost%20our%20NAD%20levels.%3Cp%3EJeffrey%20Coolidge%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20young%2C%20healthy%20person%20walked%20into%20Viavi%20seeking%20an%20NAD%2B%20supplement%2C%20Donnai%20would%20probably%20recommend%20lifestyle%20tweaks%20instead%20of%20pricey%20IVs%20and%20supplements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalking%2C%20eating%20meat%20and%20fish%2C%20nuts%2C%20fortified%20breakfast%20cereal%2C%20broccoli%2C%20and%20even%20cucumbers%20can%20help%20to%20boost%20your%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20a%20little%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20about%20living%20the%20perfect%20life%2C%20but%20it's%20about%20being%20sensible%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20supplementing%2C%26quot%3B%20Donnai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20clients%20who%20could%20benefit%20from%20NAD%20boosters%2C%20she%20recommends%20a%20powder%2C%20which%20they%20can%20mix%20into%20a%20morning%20smoothie.%20It%20costs%20%24118%20for%20a%20one-month%20supply%2C%20and%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20NR%2C%20NMN%2C%20and%20NAM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20quick%20fix%20for%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20NAD%20on%20its%20own%20doesn't%20really%20do%20much.%20It%20supports%20the%20other%20functions.%26quot%3B%20It's%20helping%20our%20bodies%20run%20properly%2C%20by%20supporting%20energy%20metabolism%2C%20keeping%20DNA%20in%20good%20repair%2C%20and%20regulating%20bone%20density%2C%20among%20other%20key%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20a%20daily%20supplement%20powder%20regimen%2C%20she%20says%20about%2010%25%20to%2015%25%20of%20clients%20don't%20end%20up%20getting%20any%20NAD%20boost%2C%20and%20their%20bloodwork%20shows%20it.%20Experts%20aren't%20yet%20sure%20exactly%20what%20is%20driving%20that%20non-response%20in%20some%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de5d2d39-594e-411e-a351-b679a3b8737e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe're%20still%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20research%20on%20NAD%20boosting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kourtney%20Kardashian%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66aab9e8aab37011780c45e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKourtney%20Kardashian%20has%20said%20she%20takes%20NAD%2B%20supplements%2C%20and%20calls%20the%20molecule%20%26quot%3Bour%20genetic%20key%20to%20longevity.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EArturo%20Holmes%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENAD%2B%20is%20booming%20in%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20London%2C%20Sonnai's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-clinics-are-next-iteration-luxury-biohack-live-longer-wealthy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elongevity%20clinic%3C%2Fa%3E%20serves%20wealthy%20clients%20who%20want%20to%20maximize%20their%20longevity%20or%20improve%20ailing%20health.%20She%20estimates%20that%20about%2030%25%20of%20them%20may%20be%20recommended%20some%20kind%20of%20NAD-boosting%20regimen%20at%20some%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20believes%20it%20can%20help%20rejuvenate%20patients%20with%20aging-related%20diseases%20or%20other%20illnesses%2C%20she%20worries%20people%20who%20don't%20actually%20need%20any%20supplemental%20NAD%20could%20overdo%20it.%20We%20don't%20know%20what%20kinds%20of%20problems%20that%20might%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20personally%20never%20advise%20anybody%20to%20take%20anything%20at%20all%20until%20you've%20measured%20whether%20you%20actually%20need%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Shalender%20Bhasin%2C%20who%20is%20conducting%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20ongoing%20clinical%20trials%20of%20NAD%20boosters%20at%20Brigham%20and%20Women's%20Hospital%20in%20Boston%2C%20says%20research%20so%20far%20has%20only%20tested%20compounds%20like%20NMN%20on%20a%20few%20hundred%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20they're%20relatively%20safe%20at%20the%20doses%20that%20have%20been%20used%2C%20and%20they%20can%20raise%20energy%20levels%20in%20the%20blood%20and%20some%20tissues%2C%20but%20not%20in%20all%20tissues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20One%20that%20hasn't%20been%20reliably%20boosted%20yet%20in%20humans%20is%20muscle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatients%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-reversed-diabetes-after-ditching-ozempic-starting-keto-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediabetes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20kidney%20disease%2C%20and%20Alzheimer's%20are%20just%20some%20of%20the%20populations%20he%20thinks%20might%20be%20able%20to%20benefit%20from%20NAD%20boosting%2C