ou%20should%20know%20if%20you%20want%20to%20quit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESmith's%20advice%20for%20people%20considering%20quitting%20their%20jobs%20is%20to%20already%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehave%20a%20budget%20and%20a%20backup%20plan%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20big%20thing%20is%20make%20sure%20you're%20ready%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHave%20a%20good%20idea%20of%20your%20expenses%20and%20your%20income%20so%20that%20you%20are%20truly%20prepared%20so%20that%20you%20don't%20find%20yourself%20having%20to%20go%20back%20to%20that%20job%20before%20you%20want%20to%2C%20if%20ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20said%20her%20backup%20plan%20was%20to%20apply%20to%20be%20a%20waitress%20or%20bartender%20instead%20of%20returning%20to%20the%20corporate%20world%20right%20away%20because%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20it%20was%20just%20not%20great%20for%20me%20mentally%2C%20emotionally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20it%20paid%20very%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20thankful%20for%20the%20benefits%20I%20got%20while%20I%20was%20there.%20I%20did%20meet%20some%20really%20good%20people%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20it's%20not%20somewhere%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20for%20the%20next%2040%20years%20of%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d84204d6-5137-4404-9601-7b0e573a06be%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Smith's%20work%20schedule%20looks%20now%20and%20the%20consequences%20of%20working%20for%20herself%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Iowa%2C%20tends%20to%20stick%20to%20a%20typical%209-to-5%20schedule%20to%20partly%20stay%20matched%20up%20with%20friends%20who%20have%20to%20work%20during%20that%20time.%20Still%2C%20she%20likes%20that%20she%20can%20get%20other%20things%20done%20beyond%20work%20within%20these%20hours.%20She%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bnice%20to%20be%20able%20to%20work%20out%2C%20read%20a%20book%2C%20run%20my%20errands%20in%20that%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20schedule%20can%20include%20kicking%20off%20the%20morning%20with%20a%20walk%20and%20reading%20on%20the%20couch.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I'm%20doing%20that%2C%20I'm%20like%2C%20oh%2C%20I%20couldn't%20be%20doing%20this%20right%20now%20if%20I%20was%20working%20my%20corporate%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20sometimes%20I%20will%20go%20sourcing%20for%20new%20inventory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20afternoons%20are%20filled%20with%20taking%20photos%20for%20reselling%20listings%20or%20edits%20for%20her%20content%20creation%20work.%20She%20said%20she%20tries%20to%20end%20her%20self-employment%20duties%20by%205%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20I%20do%20stuff%20in%20the%20evenings%3B%20while%20watching%20TV%2C%20I'll%20do%20something%20on%20my%20laptop%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20also%20try%20to%20think%2C%20OK%2C%20I%20chose%20this.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20feel%20like%20I'm%20overworking%20myself%20or%20that%20I%20have%20a%20bad%20work-life%20balance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20likes%20%26quot%3Bthe%20treasure%20hunt%26quot%3B%20of%20finding%20inexpensive%20items%20for%20her%20clothing%20reselling%20gig%20%26quot%3Band%20knowing%20that%20it's%20worth%20so%20much%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20things%20that%20I've%20found%20have%20been%20Taylor%20Swift%20t-shirts%20from%20her%20early%20tours%2C%20and%20people%20really%20like%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20pros%20of%20working%20for%20herself%20are%20being%20able%20to%20sometimes%20spend%20time%20with%20family%20members%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20day%20or%20week%20and%20feeling%20less%20stressed.%20%26quot%3BThe%20flexibility%20has%20been%20really%20nice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20definitely%20travel%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20I%20think%20I%20would%20have%20if%20I%20had%20a%20PTO%20policy%20I%20had%20to%20consider.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3