cured%20an%20all-India%20rank%20of%201%2C321%20in%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)-UG%2C%20having%20scored%20705%20out%20of%20720%20in%20NEET.%20Her%20NEET%20score%20put%20her%20in%20the%20top%2099.94%20percentile%2C%20which%20typically%20gets%20a%20student%20a%20seat%20in%20one%20of%20the%20top%20medical%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20aspiring%20doctors%20are%20required%20to%20clear%20this%20exam%20to%20get%20into%20medical%20courses%20across%20the%20country%2C%20though%20board%20marks%20also%20hold%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20March%20board%20exam%2C%20she%20managed%20only%2031%20(out%20of%20100)%20marks%20in%20chemistry%20(theory)%20and%2021%20in%20physics%20(theory)%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20Secondary%20and%20Higher%20Secondary%20Board%20(GSEB)%20exam.%20She%20barely%20passed%20in%20biology%20(theory)%20with%2039%20marks%2C%20her%20marksheet%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20supplementary%20exams%2C%20she%20scored%2022%20in%20physics%20and%20got%20just%20the%20passing%20marks%20of%2033%20in%20chemistry.%20Her%20boards%20and%20NEET%20marksheets%20went%20viral%20after%20the%20centre-wise%20and%20city-wise%20NEET-UG%20results%20were%20declared%20-%20both%20having%20the%20same%20first%2C%20middle%2C%20and%20last%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20NEET%20results%20will%20not%20help%20her%20get%20a%20seat%20in%20any%20medical%20college%20in%20the%20country%20due%20to%20her%20poor%20marks%20in%20board%20exams.%20Her%20NEET%20score%20has%20also%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20amid%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leak%20and%20grace%20marks%20awarded%20to%20some%20students%20in%20the%20NEET%20exam%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20complaint%2C%20a%20total%20of%201%2C500%20students%20were%20given%20grace%20marks.%20The%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20tasked%20with%20conducting%20the%20nationwide%20exam%2C%20had%20formed%20a%20grievance%20redressal%20panel%20which%20had%20awarded%20grace%20marks