CnAs%20per%20the%20rules%2C%20athletes%20with%20Differences%20in%20Sex%20Development%20(DSD)%20are%20currently%20eligible%20to%20compete%20in%20women's%20competition%20at%20the%20Olympics.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20DSD%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThese%20are%20a%20group%20of%20rare%20conditions%20that%20involve%20genes%2C%20hormones%20and%20reproductive%20organs.%20Some%20of%20the%20people%20with%20DSDs%20are%20raised%20as%20female%2C%20however%2C%20they%20have%20XY%20sex%20chromosomes%2C%20while%20their%20blood%20testosterone%20levels%20are%20in%20the%20male%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Algeria's%20Khelif%20was%20disqualified%20hours%20before%20her%20gold-medal%20bout%20in%20the%20world%20championships%20in%20New%20Delhi%20as%20she%20fell%20foul%20of%20International%20Boxing%20Association%20(IBA)%20eligibility%20rules%2C%20which%20do%20not%20allow%20athletes%20with%20XY%20chromosomes%20to%20compete%20in%20women's%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20she's%20been%20allowed%20to%20compete%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20last%20year%2C%20the%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20(IOC)%20stripped%20the%20International%20Boxing%20Association%20(IBA)%20of%20its%20status%20as%20the%20global%20governing%20body%20for%20boxing%20as%20it%20failed%20to%20complete%20reforms%20on%20governance%2C%20finance%20and%20ethical%20issues%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20IOC%20is%20now%20running%20the%20boxing%20competition%20at%20the%20Paris%20Games%20and%20its%20rules%20on%20inclusion%20of%20the%20athletes%20with%20DSDs%20as%20well%20as%20gender%20diversity%20in%20the%20women's%20competition%20apply.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Imane%20Khelif%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%2025-year-old%20hails%20from%20the%20Tiaret%20city%20of%20Algeria%20and%20is%20also%20the%20UNICEF%20ambassador%20at%20present.%20While%20her%20father%20did%20not%20%26quot%3Bapprove%20of%20boxing%20for%20girls%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20decided%20to%20inspire%20the%20next%20generation%20by%20winning%20a%20gold%20medal%20on%20grand%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20made%20her%20debut%20as%20a%20professional%20in%20the%202018%20World%20Championships%20and%20finished%2017th.%20During%20the%202019%20edition%20of%20the%20event%2C%20she%20came%20in%2019th%20position.%20In%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics%20in%202021%2C%20she%20was%20knocked%20out%20by%20Ireland's%20Kellie%20Harrington%20in%20the%20quarter-finals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20social%20media%20outrage%20over%20her%20eligibility%2C%20the%20IOC%20defended%20Khelif%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20athletes%20participating%20in%20the%20boxing%20tournament%20of%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20Paris%202024%20comply%20with%20the%20competition's%20eligibility%20and%20entry%20regulations%2C%20as%20well%20as%20all%20applicable%20medical%20regulations%20set%20by%20the%20Paris%202024%20Boxing%20Unit%20(PBU).%20As%20with%20previous%20Olympic%20boxing%20competitions%2C%20the%20gender%20and%20age%20of%20the%20athletes%20are%20based%20on%20their%20passports.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhelif%20is%20competing%20in%20the%20women's%20category%20in%20the%2066kg%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722584040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F60a7divo_jk-rowling_625x300_29_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fauthor-jk-rowlings-courts-controversy-after-comment-on-algerian-boxer-imane-khelif-6246094%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Harry%20Potter%20creator%20JK%20Rowling%20has%20courted%20controversy%20after%20she%20referred%20to%20Algerian%20boxer%20Imane%20Khelif%20as%20a%20man.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fauthor-jk-rowlings-courts-controversy-after-comment-on-algerian-boxer-imane-khelif-6246094%22