Ms.%20Benett%20had%20been%20feeling%20unwell%20for%20several%20years%20and%20had%20repeatedly%20sought%20medical%20intervention%E2%80%A6%20She%20was%20offered%20no%20support%20or%20suggestions%20about%20her%20ill%20health%20beyond%20weight%20loss.%20When%20the%20root%20of%20her%20malaise%20was%20eventually%20identified%20as%20an%20inoperable%20cancer%2C%20Ms.%20Bennett%20was%20given%20just%20days%20to%20live%3C%2Fi%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20opening%20statement%20of%20a%20study%20published%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Cu%3E%3Ca%20data-linkindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-auth%3D%5C%22VerificationFailed%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapc01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com%2F%3Furl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%252Fpmc%252Farticles%252FPMC10996856%252F%26data%3D05%257C02%257CHarshitaM%2540ndtv.com%257C83796ffb12784663c51208dcb226c95f%257C89e0013190cd478790cc5ded788d77de%257C0%257C0%257C638581126864600006%257CUnknown%257CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%253D%257C0%257C%257C%257C%26sdata%3DuQ%252Bi4N%252BCZIzXNQ%252BRz6Sfo%252BS0kuJly%252FjFKnvCjUNhn9Q%253D%26reserved%3D0%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Original%20URL%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10996856%2F.%20Click%20or%20tap%20if%20you%20trust%20this%20link.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Library%20For%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%2C%20which%20documented%20the%20medical%20struggles%20of%20%E2%80%98fat%20women'.%20Only%2C%20this%20struggle%20is%20not%20with%20being%20fat%20or%20obese%2C%20but%20with%20getting%20a%20diagnosis%20for%20other%20diseases%20as%20a%20woman%20who%20exists%20in%20a%20fat%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Gods'%2C%20As%20Flawed%20As%20Humans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20not%20to%20compare%20doctors%20and%20medical%20professionals%20with%20Gods%20when%20they%20do%20so%20much%20to%20help%20people%20and%20save%20lives.%20However%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20treating%20%E2%80%98fat'%20bodies%2C%20we%20are%20often%20reminded%20that%20these%20Gods%20are%20as%20flawed%20and%20prejudiced%20as%20humans.%20I%20learnt%20this%20the%20hard%20way%2C%20when%20after%20months%20(years%2C%20actually)%20of%20pain%2C%20dysfunction%2C%20and%20poor%20physical%20health%2C%20I%20was%20returned%20home%20by%20multiple%20doctors%20who%20simply%20couldn't%20see%20beyond%20my%20weight.%20None%20of%20the%2011%20doctors%20I%20visited%20across%20Delhi%20and%20Patna%20bothered%20to%20see%20past%20my%20weight%20and%20look%20for%20disorders%20that%20weren't%20weight-related.%20Even%20with%20blood%20reports%20suggestive%20of%20something%20very%20serious%2C%20the%20only%20advice%20I%20was%20given%20was%20to%20%E2%80%98lose%20weight'.%20Finally%2C%20in%20Delhi%2C%20I%20asked%20a%20doctor%2C%20%E2%80%9CIs%20it%20really%20the%20weight%3F%20Am%20I%20that%20fat%20that%20I%20am%20really%20the%20cause%20of%20all%20my%20problems%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20will%20never%20forget%20the%20face%2C%20the%20kind%20eyes%2C%20as%20he%20told%20me%20this%3A%20%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20I%20think%20you%20have%20a%20tumour%2C%20but%20maybe%20not%20cancer%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20get%20you%20tested%20ASAP%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20this%20with%20all%20the%20calm%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2011%20months%2C%20I%20went%20through%2016%20sonographies%2C%2030-odd%20blood%20tests%2C%20and%20dozens%20of%20appointments%20with%20specialists.%20I%20waited%20in%20waiting%20halls%20enough%20to%20surpass%20my%20reading%20goals%20(I%20read%2060%20books%20that%20year%2C%20instead%20of%20the%2052%20I%20had%20promised%20myself).%20The%20pain%20never%20left%20my%20side%20though%20as%20I%20fought%20the%20blackouts%2C%20dizzy%20spells%2C%20and%20the%20dark%20clouds%20that%20would%20form%20over%20my%20eyes%2C%20brain%2C%20and%20soul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Doctors%20See%20What%20They%20Want%20To%20See%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20doctor%20and%20his%20suggestion%20led%20me%20to%20question%20the%20very%20ethics%20of%20medical%20practice.%20Obesity%20is%20a%20serious%20problem%20and%20can%20lead%20to%20multiple%20health%20issues.%20However%2C%20most%20doctors%20in%20India%20have%20an%20inherent%20weight%20bias%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20their%20patients%2C%20especially%20women.%20My%20former%20gynaecologists%20made%20me%20go%20through%20nearly%2010%20ultrasounds%20to%20confirm%20that%20I%20had%20PCOS%20(which%20I%20did%20not%2C%20and%20I%20kept%20insisting%20I%20didn't%20have%20it)%20because%20in%20their%20words%2C%20not%20being%20skinny%20naturally%20meant%20having%20%E2%80%98fat'-related%20health%20issues%20or%20lifestyle%20diseases.%20Because%20if%20you%20are%20fat%2C%20you%20must%20have%20a%20poor%20diet%20consisting%20of%20junk%20and%20fried%20food.%20No%20matter%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20happen%20to%20be%20quite%20conscious%20about%20my%20diet.%20I%20cook%20all%20my%20meals%2C%20try%20to%20balance%20all%20nutrients.%20And%20so%2C%20this%20implication%20by%20doctors%20irked%20me%20deeply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20dug%20deeper%20and%20came%20across%20women%20from%20various%20regions%2C%20ages%2C%20and%20backgrounds%20who%20had%20been%20denied%20proper%20medical%20care%20because%20their%20doctors%20couldn't%20see%20beyond%20their%20weight.%20I%20found%20their%20stories%20in%20the%20nooks%20and%20crannies%20of%20the%20internet%2C%20via%20Reddit%20or%20Instagram%20or%20online%20blogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20last%20night%2C%20I%20spoke%20with%20my%20doctor%2C%20the%20one%20who%20had%20cared%20to%20look%20beyond%20my%20physical%20appearance%3A%20Dr%20Sanchayan%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20there%20might%20be%20a%20subconscious%20bias%20that%20may%20lead%20to%20ignoring%20issues%20of%20larger%20bodies%2C%20but%20I%20cannot%20say%20it%20is%20intentional%2C%E2%80%9D%20Roy%20says.%20He%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%20that%20%E2%80%9Cobesity%20definitely%20overshadows%E2%80%9D%20individual%20symptoms%20and%20that%20a%20few%20medical%20professionals%20may%20give%20in%20to%20the%20presumption%20that%20a%20fat%20body%20necessarily%20has%20obesity-related%20issues.%20It's%20a%20double%20whammy%20for%20women%2C%20who%20often%20get%20a%20mixed%20misdiagnosis%2C%20centred%20around%20%E2%80%9Cperiods%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20is%2C%20menstrual%20health%2C%20and%20obesity.%20These%20women%20are%20told%20that%20their%20issues%20are%20a%20function%20of%20their%20menstrual%20cycles%2C%20which%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20can%20be%20fixed%20by%20just%20being%20thin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Gendered%20Experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20Roy%20whether%20this%20bias%2C%20the%20fixation%20on%20%E2%80%98womanly'%20issues%2C%20existed%20for%20all%20sizes%20of%20women%2C%C2%A0%20Roy%20said%20something%20peculiar.%20%E2%80%9CMen%20definitely%20are%20easier%20to%20diagnose%2C%20they%20are%20a%20lot%20more%20clear%20with%20their%20communications%20and%20forthcoming%20with%20all%20issues%2C%20even%20embarrassing%20symptoms%2C%20so%20fatter%20men%20are%20not%20as%20difficult%20to%20diagnose%20as%20women%E2%80%9D%20(I%20was%2C%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20ready%20to%20lose%20faith%20in%20a%20doctor%20I%20had%20come%20to%20trust%20after%20a%20string%20of%20discomfiting%20medical%20experiences).%20But%2C%20he%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20what%20the%20woman%20thinks%20of%20her%20issues%20is%20coloured%20by%20how%20her%20family%20or%20maybe%20a%20partner%20perceives%20them.%20If%20someone%20close%20to%20her%20readily%20dismisses%20her%20pain%20or%20minimises%20her%20issues%2C%20or%20lets%20her%20believe%20that%20all%20women%20go%20through%20similar%20pain%2C%20she%20may%20not%20feel%20that%20it%20is%20something%20major.%E2%80%9D%20I%20sighed%20with%20relief%20at%20his%20addendum%2C%20because%20what%20he%20said%20was%20true.%20Roy%20emphasised%20that%20this%20ostensible%20lack%20of%20communication%20was%20gender-based%20and%20that%20women%20often%20did%20not%20open%20up%20to%20a%20male%20diagnostician%20due%20to%20cultural%20conditioning.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20shared%20this%20experience%20on%20Instagram%20some%20time%20ago%2C%20a%20follower%20reached%20out%20to%20me%20with%20one%20of%20the%20most%20harrowing%20misdiagnosis%20stories.%20Her%20aunt%20had%20been%20going%20through%20intense%20pain%20in%20her%20breast%2C%20which%20didn't%20even%20let%20her%20move%20sometimes.%20Not%20surprisingly%2C%20the%20doctor%20told%20her%20to%20lose%20weight.%20Another%20told%20her%20that%20her%20heavy%20weight%20meant%20that%20she%20had%20heavier%20breasts%2C%20and%20that%20was%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20pain.%20Many%20doctors%20followed%2C%20and%20they%20all%20offered%20similar%20explanations.%20In%202020%2C%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20breast%20cancer.%20The%20diagnosis%20came%20at%20the%20final%20stage%20of%20the%20disease%2C%20meaning%2C%20not%20much%20could%20be%20done%20by%20then%20to%20help%20her.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20it%20possible%20an%20early%20diagnosis%20could%20have%20helped%20her%3F%20If%20the%20doctors%20saw%20beyond%20the%20weight%3F%E2%80%9D%20her%20niece%20said%20to%20me.%20I%20wonder%20the%20same.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E28-Year-Old%20Tanishka's%20Story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20close%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20one%20of%20the%20liveliest%2C%20most%20fun%20people%20I%20know%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20an%20ocean%20of%20empathy%2C%20intelligence%2C%20and%2C%20as%20Gen%20Z%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9Cvibes%E2%80%9D%2C%20lost%20so%20much%20of%20herself%20in%20the%20process%20of%20getting%20a%20reliable%20diagnosis.%20Here%20is%2028-year-old%20Tanishka's%20story%2C%20in%20her%20words%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BI'll%20talk%20specifically%20about%20my%20back%20injury.%20I%20had%20been%20having%20pain%20for%20over%20a%20year%20%5Bduring%202022%5D%20before%20I%20decided%20to%20consult%20a%20doctor.%20I%20was%20already%20afraid%20of%20going%20to%20one%20because%20of%20how%20dismissive%20they%20are%20to%20bodies%20like%20mine.%20I%20consulted%20them%20only%20when%20the%20pain%20got%20really%20bad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20doctors%20told%20me%20it%20was%20nothing%20and%20that%20I'd%20have%20to%20reduce%20my%20weight.%20One%20assumed%20that%20I%20don't%20exercise%3B%20most%20do%2C%20and%20it%20is%20all%20quite%20demeaning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20after%20a%20year%2C%20I%20had%20an%20episode%20%5Bend%20of%202022%5D%20where%20a%20sharp%20pain%20made%20me%20collapse.%20I%20had%20to%20be%20hospitalised%2C%20and%20an%20MRI%20was%20done.%C2%A0%20That's%20when%20I%20learnt%20that%20a%20couple%20of%20my%20discs%20were%20damaged.%20The%20assumptions%20doctors%20had%20about%20me%20and%20my%20lifestyle%20and%20their%20diagnosis%20being%20limited%20to%20my%20size%20let%20this%20huge%20issue%20go%20unnoticed.%20I%20grew%20very%20scared%20to%20move%20and%20suffered%20a%20lot%20of%20trauma%20from%20the%20injury%2C%20which%20I%20continue%20to%20battle%20with.%20After%20the%20diagnosis%2C%20I%20didn't%20step%20out%20of%20the%20house%20for%20three%20months%20because%20I%20was%20so%20paranoid%20about%20feeling%20that%20pain%20again.%20I%20was%20on%20painkillers%20during%20these%20three%20months%2C%20when%20I%20should've%20been%20moving%20my%20body%20to%20heal.%20I've%20lost%20time%20and%20confidence%20and%20faith%20in%20medical%20facilities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeeking%20Confirmation%20For%20A%20Disease%20I%20Didn't%20Have%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20that%20a%20long%20time%20ago%2C%20in%202012%2C%20I%20was%20put%20on%20a%20three-year%20course%20of%20life-saving%20heavy%20steroids.%20And%2C%20no%20prizes%20for%20guessing%2C%20they%20led%20to%20weight%20gain.%20Until%20then%2C%20as%20long%20as%20I%20was%20skinny%2C%20the%20medical%20fraternity%20had%20been%20all%20too%20happy%20to%20look%20at%20my%20problems%2C%20listen%20to%20my%20symptoms%2C%20and%20even%20brainstorm%20with%20an%20international%20colleague%20to%20save%20me.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20changed%20as%20soon%20as%20my%20body%20started%20to%20grow%20bigger.%20Now%2C%20all%20my%20symptoms%20had%20to%20be%20double-%2C%20triple-%2C%20quadruple-checked%20with%20tests%20worth%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20rupees%2C%20all%20to%20ensure%20that%20my%20symptoms%20were%20real%20and%20not%20mere%20imaginations%20of%20a%20'fat'%20woman.%20When%20I%20was%2040%20kilograms%20and%20said%20that%20I%20was%20suffering%20from%20acute%20pain%20in%20my%20stomach%2C%20bones%20or%20pelvis%2C%20the%20doctors%20were%20sympathetic%20and%20believed%20me.%C2%A0When%20I%20became%20a%20lot%2C%20lot%20heavier%20and%20complained%20of%20pain%20in%20my%20pelvis%20area%2C%2011%20different%20doctors%20across%20the%20best%20of%20hospitals%20and%20clinics%20in%20the%20country%20told%20me%20that%20because%20I%20was%20fat%2C%20I%20had%20PCOS.%20Other%20than%20my%20weight%2C%20there%20was%20no%20other%20evidence%20for%20it.%20Yet%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20pay%20close%20to%20Rs%2030%2C000-35%2C000%20in%20a%20year%20to%20seek%20confirmation%20for%20a%20disease%20that%20I%20did%20not%20have.%C2%A0%20All%20reports%20said%20that%20I%20did%20not%20have%20PCOS%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20all%20doctors%20were%20convinced%20that%20my%20medical%20issues%20had%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98fat'-related.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20doctor%20ever%20cared%20to%20look%20at%20my%20body%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20beyond%20the%20layer%20of%20fat%20that%20envelops%20it.%20No%20doctor%20cared%20to%20look%20at%20my%20brain%20and%20get%20it%20scanned.%20Until%20finally%2C%20one%20did.%20And%20what%20if%20I%20had%20believed%20those%20numerous%20others%20earlier%3F%20What%20if%20I%20had%20gone%20on%20trying%20to%20lose%20weight%2C%20starved%20myself%20in%20my%20desperation%20to%20get%20skinny%20and%20%E2%80%98better'%3F%20How%20long%20-%20or%20late%20-%20would%20it%20have%20been%20before%20I%20would%20come%20to%20know%20of%20the%20pea-sized%20invader%20making%20me%20sick%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Anwiti%20Singh%20is%20Assistant%20Producer%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722580680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F7h4p8ag_fat-_625x300_02_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fhow-11-doctors-failed-to-diagnose-my-a-fat-womans-tumour-6245824%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22No%20doctor%20ever%20cared%20to%20look%20at%20my%20body%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20beyond%20the%20layer%20of%20fat%20that%20envelops%20it.%20No%20doctor%20cared%20to%20look%20at%20my%20brain%20and%20get%20it%20scanned.%20Until%20one%20did%20and%20found%20a%20tumour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Fhow-11-doctors-failed-to-diagnose-my-a-fat-womans-tumour-6245824%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Camera%2C%20Iron%20Gate%20Falls%20On%203-Year-Old%20Pune%20Girl%2C%20She%20Dies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20three-and-a-half-year-old%20girl%20died%20after%20an%20iron%20gate%20fell%20on%20her%20while%20she%20was%20playing%20with%20other%20children%20in%20Pune's%20Pimpri-Chinchwad%20area%20On%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20footage%20installed%20in%20the%20locality%20captured%20the%20moment%20when%20the%20gate%20crushed%20the%20child%2C%20killing%20her%20on%20the%20spot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20victim%2C%20Girija%20Ganesh%20Shinde%2C%20was%20playing%20with%20her%20friends%20in%20her%20neighbourhood%20in%20the%20afternoon.%20As%20they%20were%20playing%2C%20two%20children%20entered%20the%20space%20behind%20the%20gate%20while%20Girija%20and%20another%20child%20stood%20in%20front%20of%20it.%20When%20one%20of%20the%20children%20standing%20behind%20the%20gate%20started%20pulling%20it%2C%20it%20fell%20squarely%20on%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20DCP%20Shivani%20Pawar%2C%20an%20accidental%20death%20report%20has%20been%20registered%20while%20the%20police%20are%20investigating%20the%20CCTV%20footage%20and%20checking%20from%20all%20angles%20why%20the%20gate%2C%20which%20weighs%20hundreds%20of%20kilograms%2C%20fell.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722580440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F54g5cqgg_pune-girl-dies-_625x300_02_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpune-news%2Fon-camera-iron-gate-falls-on-3-year-old-pune-girl-she-dies-6245765%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20three-and-a-half-year-old%20girl%20died%20after%20an%20iron%20gate%20fell%20on%20her%20while%20she%20was%20playing%20with%20other%20children%20in%20Pune's%20Pimpri-Chinchwad%20area%20On%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpune-news%2Fon-camera-iron-gate-falls-on-3-year-old-pune-girl-she-dies-6245765%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpune-news%2Fon-camera-iron-gate-falls-on-3-year-old-pune-girl-she-dies-6245765%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpune-news%2Fon-camera-iron-gate-falls-on-3-year-old-pune-girl-she-dies-6245765%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kabir%20Khan%2C%20Imtiaz%20Ali%2C%20Rima%20Das%20and%20Onir%E2%80%99s%20IFFM%20Opener%20%E2%80%98My%20Melbourne%E2%80%99%20Unveils%20Trailer%20(EXCLUSIVE)%20%E2%80%93%20Global%20Bulletin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722580250000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FMy-Melbourne.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236093694%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MIGRANT%20MOSAIC%20A%20trailer%