%20of%20the%20NEET%20exam%2C%20which%20was%20held%20on%20May%205%20but%20ran%20into%20trouble%20a%20month%20later%2C%20when%20results%20were%20declared.%20Such%20%26quot%3Bflip-flops%26quot%3B%20do%20not%20serve%20students'%20interests%2C%20the%20court%20told%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20highlighted%20all%20deficiencies%20in%20the%20structural%20processes...%20this%20we%20cannot%20afford%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20the%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20Friday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20has%20given%20the%20centre's%20committee%20-%20a%20seven-member%20panel%20led%20by%20ex-ISRO%20chief%20Dr%20K%20Radhakrishnan%20and%20including%20former%20AIIMS%20(Delhi)%20Director%20Dr%20Randeep%20Guleria%20-%20time%20till%20September%2030%20to%20present%20its%20report.%20The%20committee%20has%20been%20tasked%20with%20analysing%20the%20entire%20examination%20process%20and%20suggest%20changes%20to%20make%20it%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReport%20of%20committee%20to%20be%20submitted%20by%20September%2030%20to%20the%20government.%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20shall%20report%20compliance%20of%20committee%20and%20decision%20to%20implement%20(measures)%20in%20two%20weeks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20offered%20eight%20points%20to%20guide%20the%20committee%2C%20including%20laying%20out%20a%20standard%20operating%20procedure%2C%20or%20protocol%2C%20for%20conduct%20of%20qualifying%20exams%2C%20a%20review%20of%20process%20of%20allotting%20exam%20centres%20and%20enhanced%20identity%20checks%20of%20candidates%2C%20and%20CCTV%20monitoring%20of%20exam%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20point%20was%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bsecure%20logistics%20providers%20for%20ensuring%20non-tampering%20of%20question%20papers%26quot%3B%3B%20this%20is%20crucial%20given%20the%202024%20NEET-UG%20exam%20papers%20may%20have%20been%20leaked%20while%20they%20were%20being%20transported%20-%20in%20locked%20boxes%20-%20from%20where%20they%20were%20printed%20to%20the%20exam%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20larger%20question%20of%20leaked%20exam%20papers%2C%20the%20court%20said%20it%20was%20satisfied%20%26quot%3Bthere%20was%20no%20systemic%20breach...%20the%20leak%20was%20limited%20to%20Patna%20(in%20Bihar)%20and%20Hazaribagh%20(in%20Jharkhand)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-leak-hazaribagh-paper-leak-oasis-school-cbi-neet-ug-paper-leak-had-genesis-in-hazaribagh-zeroing-in-on-school-cbi-officials-6078152%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHazaribagh%20leak%20has%20been%20flagged%20as%20'Ground%20Zero'%20by%20the%20CBI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20been%20tasked%20with%20investigating%20a%20nation-wide%20'solver%20gang'%20racket%20that%20leaks%20question%20papers.%20The%20agency%20has%20made%20multiple%20arrests%20since%2C%20including%20a%20man%20called%20Rakesh%20Ranjan%2C%20alias%20Rocky%2C%20the%20alleged%20kingpin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-paper-leak-case-cbi-arrests-rajesh-ranjan-alias-rocky-cbi-arrests-rocky-alleged-mastermind-in-neet-ug-paper-leak-case-6083484%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBI%20Arrests%20'Rocky'%2C%20Alleged%20Mastermind%20In%20NEET%20Paper%20Leak%20Case%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20agency%20has%20also%20filed%20its%20first%20chargesheet%20in%20this%20case.%20It%20has%20named%2013%20people%2C%20including%20four%20candidates%2C%20a%20junior%20engineer%20and%20two%20individuals%20labelled%20as%20'kingpins'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcandidates-parents-kingpins-named-in-cbis-1st-neet-chargesheet-6242838%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECandidates%2C%20Parents%2C%20'Kingpins'%20Named%20In%20CBI's%2