%20in%20the%20affected%20areas%20to%20stay%20on%20alert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescue%20operation%20is%20also%20underway%20in%20Malana%20where%20several%20people%20are%20trapped%20in%20a%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722576900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fqn4hqo6o_uttarakhand-landslide_625x300_02_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-himachal-search-for-cloudburst-survivors-brace-for-more-rain-6245473%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cloudbursts%20in%20the%20twin%20Himalayan%20states%20of%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20have%20claimed%20over%20a%20dozen%20lives%20since%20yesterday%20as%20rescuers%20scrambled%20this%20morning%20to%20search%20for%20survivors%20in%20the%20mountains.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-himachal-search-for-cloudburst-survivors-brace-for-more-rain-6245473%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-himachal-search-for-cloudburst-survivors-brace-for-more-rain-6245473%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-himachal-search-for-cloudburst-survivors-brace-for-more-rain-6245473%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Started%20as%20a%20Hobby%2C%20Kerala%20Engineer%E2%80%99s%20Vibrant%20Portulaca%20Flower%20Garden%20Earns%20Rs%201%20Lakh%2FMonth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20exhausting%20week%20at%20her%20workplace%20in%20Kochi%2C%20Parvathy%20Mohanan%20comes%20back%20to%20her%20quaint%20hometown%20in%20the%20scenic%20locale%20of%20Muhamma%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Alappuzha%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20engineer%E2%80%99s%20weekend%20starts%20with%20admiring%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282824%2F