ture.%20She%20also%20encourages%20others%20to%20opt%20for%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyone%20in%20need%20of%20additional%20income%20can%20do%20this%20as%20a%20business%20also.%20The%20key%20is%20to%20grow%20low-maintenance%20but%20high%20demand%20plants%20like%20portulaca%20and%20find%20a%20trustworthy%20team%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20work%20in%20your%20absence%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajani%20Mohanan%2C%20who%20has%20seen%20Parvathy%20toil%20hard%20while%20managing%20both%20the%20office%20and%20the%20farm%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20started%20this%20business%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20when%20she%20was%20just%20a%20college%20student.%20This%20has%20become%20an%20extra%20source%20of%20income%20for%20her%20and%20she%20is%20able%20to%20manage%20all%20her%20expenses%20with%20ease%20and%20have%20some%20left%20for%20enjoyment%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Parvathy%20returns%20to%20Kochi%20for%20her%20work%2C%20Rajani%20takes%20over%20some%20of%20her%20responsibilities%20here%20like%20helping%20with%20order%20packaging.%20She%20shares%20how%20the%20business%20has%20also%20helped%20them%20bond%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParvathy%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20not%20just%20one%20of%20entrepreneurial%20success%20but%20also%20a%20lesson%20in%20pursuing%20one%E2%80%99s%20passion%20against%20the%20odds.%20Her%20journey%20from%20a%20hobbyist%20to%20a%20successful%20entrepreneur%20highlights%20the%20potential%20of%20turning%20a%20simple%20passion%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348172%2Fflower-farmer-in-karnataka-bengaluru-srikanth-bollapally-grows-roses-gerbera-carnations-making-crores-annually%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethriving%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20her%20story%20continues%20to%20unfold%2C%20one%20bloom%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20compliments%20and%20appre