ika-panchayat-1-1722331421.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-1-1722331421-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-1-1722331421-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-1-1722331421-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-1-1722331421-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359005%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20programme%2C%20spearheaded%20by%20IAS%20Minal%20Karanwal%2C%20has%20been%20empowering%20young%20rural%20girls.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinal%20identified%2060%20active%20gram%20panchayats%20in%20Nanded%20and%20conducted%20an%20orientation%20session.%20At%20least%20five%20young%20girls%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2011%20to%2018%20years%20in%20each%2060%20panchayats%20were%20identified%20to%20make%20a%20model%20%E2%80%98Balika%20Panchayat%E2%80%99%20that%20mimics%20a%20regular%20gram%20panchayat%20with%20five%20officeholders.%20Among%20these%2C%20one%20acts%20as%20a%20sarpanch%20(village%20head).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20slate%20was%20wide%20open%20and%20I%20asked%20them%20to%20write%20on%20it%20as%20they%20wished.%20I%20gave%20them%20a%20period%20of%20three%20months%20to%20implement%20the%20project%20on%20ground%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsidering%20their%20broad%20objective%2C%20they%20took%20most%20initiatives%20such%20as%20organising%20cleanliness%20drives%20in%20the%20village%2C%20getting%20the%20numbers%20and%20names%20fixed%20up%20on%20the%20members%20in%20the%20gram%20panchayats%2C%20organising%20meetings%20(gram%20sabhas)%2C%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20girls%20started%20an%20enti