8%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThese%20girls%20also%20take%20up%20initiatives%20such%20as%20organising%20cleanliness%20drives%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20at%20least%20300%20such%20girls%20in%20Nanded%20are%20taking%20leadership%20roles%20to%20eradicate%20ill-practices%20from%20their%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20women%20take%20charge%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinal%20conducts%20monthly%20review%20meetings%20to%20check%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20initiative.%20She%20has%20also%20created%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20comprising%20the%20village%20heads.%20%E2%80%9CI%20constantly%20read%20their%20messages%20and%20appreciate%20their%20work%20to%20boost%20them.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20give%20them%20some%20challenges%20to%20perform%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20impact%20of%20the%20work%20is%20that%20these%20young%20girls%20between%2011%20and%2018%20years%20have%20started%20demanding%20their%20rights%20from%20the%20government.%20They%20have%20started%20questioning%20authorities%20why%20eggs%20were%20not%20given%20in%20the%20mid-day%20meals%2C%20or%20holding%20them%20accountable%20for%20conducting%20regular%20health%20camps%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20even%20asking%20why%20bicycles%20aren%E2%80%99t%20given%20to%20reach%20far-off%20schools.%20The%20initiation%20of%20such%20a%20conversation%20itself%20is%20a%20success%20for%20us.%20These%20girls%20tell%20me%20how%20villagers%20have%20started%20listening%20to%20them.%20Just%20developing%20such%20leadership%20was%20my%20ultimate%20aim%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-3-1722331589.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20girls%20door-to-door%20to%20motivate%20people%20and%20explain%20the%20ill-effects%20of%20consuming%20liquor%2C%20regular%20consumption%20of%20necessary%20drugs%2C%20and%20more.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-3-1722331589.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-3-1722331589-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-3-1722331589-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-3-1722331589-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FBalika-panchayat-3-1722331589-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359008%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20girls%20door-to-door%20to%20motivate%20people%20about%20regular%20consumption%20of%20necessary%20drugs%20and%20explain%20the%20ill-effects%20of%20consuming%20liquor.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20feat%20has%20not%20been%20easier%20for%20the%20administration.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20idea%20of%20empowerment%20is%20least%20understood%20in%20villages.%20They%20question%20why%20they%20should%20invest%20in%20this%20project%20as%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20an%20asset%20building%20program%20in%20the%20tangible%20sense%2C%20nobody%20is%20building%20a%20road%2C%20nobody%20is%20getting%20somebody%20to%20inaugurate%20it.%20There%20is%20no%20funding%20attached%20to%20the%20project.%20So%2C%20people%20naturally%20take%20less%20interest%20in%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Minal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20identify%20people%20who%20are%20motivated%20at%20the%20human%20resource%20front%2C%20who%20understand%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20build%20a%20h