0the%20river.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357468%2Fias-officer-revive-water-table-cdo-varanasi-himanshu-nagpal-rainwater-harvesting-river-rejuvenation-groundwater-recharge%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20IAS%20officer%20decided%20to%20rejuvenate%20the%20river%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20shares%20how%20the%20district%20administration%20revived%20the%20river%20to%20its%20old%20glory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20masterplan%20behind%20the%20river%20rejuvenation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpearheaded%20by%20Manish%2C%20the%20Sambhal%20district%20conducted%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20length%20of%20the%20river.%20The%20results%20showed%20that%20the%20Sot%20river%2C%20which%20appeared%20to%20be%20non-existent%2C%20was%20actually%20a%20110%20km%20long%20stretch%20starting%20from%20the%20Amroha%20district%20in%20the%20North%20and%20flowing%20towards%20Budaun%20in%20the%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20the%20administration%20conducted%20a%20survey%20to%20understand%20the%20natural%20alignment%20of%20the%20river.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20physical%20demarcation%20of%20the%20region%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20the%20river.%20The%20third%20step%20was%20to%20clear%20the%20illegal%20encroachments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20major%20challenges%20was%20to%20remove%20the%20encroachments%20along%20the%20river.%20Using%20the%20revenue%20land%20records%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20there%20were%20huge%20encroachments%20on%20the%20river%20area%20which%20had%20become%20flat%20at%20some%20points.%20Although%20there%20was%20no%20permanent%20construction%2C%20people%20started%20using%20it%20to%20grow%20crops.%20As%20it%20was%20illegal%20usage%2C%20we%20sought%20the%20help